OL,3,CTributes paid to football coach who
OL,4,Cdied following Christmas Eve crash
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a
OL,7,Fchildren's football coach who died
OL,8,Ffollowing a crash on Christmas Eve.
OL,10,FJust before 8.40pm, a black Ford Puma
OL,11,Fand a grey Audi A4 were involved in a
OL,12,Fcrash at the junction of East
OL,13,FLancashire Road and Stonebridge Lane
OL,14,Fin Liverpool.
OL,16,FStephen Jones, 33, from Bootle, who
OL,17,Fwas driving the Ford Puma, was taken
OL,18,Fto hospital after the crash with
OL,19,Fsignificant injuries and died on
OL,20,FSaturday, January 3.
