OL,6,FA 34-year-old woman, who is Stephen's
OL,7,Fpartner, remains in a serious but
OL,8,Fstable condition in hospital.
OL,10,FTheir eight-year-old son suffered
OL,11,Fminor injuries and is being cared for
OL,12,Fby his wider family.
OL,14,FMerseyside Police said Stephen's
OL,15,Ffamily are being supported by
OL,16,Fspecially trained family liaison
OL,17,Fofficers.
