OL,6,FIn a tribute, Stephen's family have
OL,7,Fsaid: "Stephen was a loving son,
OL,8,Fbrother, partner, uncle but most
OL,9,Fimportantly a dad, a role that meant
OL,10,Fthe world to him.
OL,12,F"A friend and a lifelong Everton
OL,13,Fsupporter who was filled to his core
OL,14,Fwith a passion to help people.
OL,16,F"His love for coaching children's
OL,17,Fgrassroots football meant he made a
OL,18,Fdifference in so many lives.
OL,19,F"Stephen's death will leave a void for
OL,20,Fmany people that won't ever be filled.
