OL,6,F"He will be missed deeply but loved
OL,7,Fforever and always in our hearts."
OL,9,FPolice have arrested a 32-year-old man
OL,10,Ffrom Liverpool on suspicion of causing
OL,11,Fdeath by dangerous driving, causing
OL,12,Fserious injury by dangerous driving
OL,13,Fand driving whilst unfit through drink
OL,14,For drugs.
OL,16,FHe has been bailed as the
OL,17,Finvestigation continues.JDetective
OL,18,FSergeant Simon Duffy from the Serious
OL,19,FCollision Investigation unit said:
OL,20,F"Our thoughts remain with Stephen's
OL,21,Ffamily at this tragic time.
