OL,6,F"We will continue to support them
OL,7,Fthroughout this investigation and seek
OL,8,Fto provide the answers that they need.
OL,10,F"Stephen's family and friends are
OL,11,Fdevastated. Stephen was clearly loved
OL,12,Fby those closest to him and his loss
OL,13,Fis felt much wider across the local
OL,14,Farea due to his involvement in
OL,15,Fcoaching children's football.
OL,17,F"Although a man has been arrested,
OL,18,Fthis is a fast moving investigation
OL,19,Fwith numerous lines of enquiry being
OL,20,Ffollowed.
