OL,6,FEye witness accounts and dashcam are
OL,7,Fkey to the investigation and I would
OL,8,Furge anyone travelling in the area of
OL,9,Fthe M57 or the East Lancashire Road,
OL,10,Fat around 8.30pm on Christmas Eve, to
OL,11,Fcontact my team as soon as possible.
OL,13,F"I would also like to thank members of
OL,14,Fthe public that stopped at the scene,
OL,15,Fto provide first aid and assisted the
OL,16,Femergency services."
